Job Description
We need scientific writers who are:1. Good in written English 2. Expertise in MS Office 3. Good/error-less typing 4. Ability of identifying errors in written text and making necessary corrections 5. This is office based work where typing and editing of text will be required. 6. Occasionally converting proposed ideas into well formatted text will also be required. 7. Flexible timing can be offered, and depending upon performance tasks can be assigned to be completed at own place (if desired) 8. The job is contractual and will be terminated upon completion of project.
Job Specification
Typing, drafting and occasionally creation of manuscript is required. All support and guidance will be provided.
